RootTools is a focus on the root of the user to provide convenient software. Mainly to provide the application of freezing, automated component management, depth clean-up system and other functions, but also for the current massive user MIUI system corresponding optimization. The latest version has been added xposed framework corresponding to the function, in order to achieve more powerful optimization capabilities.

The software complies with the GPLv2 protocol and is free and open source, and remains up to date. Do not accept agents, reselling, and other commercial activities, do not require donations, the right to use the software completely to the user. You can even download and modify this source, and release it under GPLv2.